Venadaparib (NOV140101) (IDX-1197) is a potent, selective and orally active PARP inhibitor with IC50s of 1.4 nM and 1.0 nM for PARP1 and PARP2, respectively. Venadaparib is insensitive to PARP-5. Vena
daparib prevents the repair of DNA single-strand breaks (SSBs) and can be used in solid tumor research.

