5-Iodotubercidin (NSC-113939) is a potent adenosine kinase inhibitor with IC50 of 26 nM. It inhibits nucleoside transporter, CK1, insulin receptor tyrosine kinase, phosphorylase kinase, PKA, CK2 and P
KC.

