>  <Product Name>  (329) 
AY 9944

>  <Short Description for web display>  (329) 
AY 9944 is a specific cholesterol biosynthesis inhibitor. AY 9944 inhibits the 7-dehydro cholesterol Delta7-reductase (DHCR7) enzyme (IC50=13 nM). At high doses, AY 9944 inhibits also in cultured embr
yos sterol Delta7-Delta8 isomerase, which causes the accumulation of cholest-8-en-3beta-ol[1][2][3]. AY 9944 causes hypocholesterolemia and accumulation of 7DHC.

