>  <Product Name>  (347) 
Pomalidomide-PEG1-C2-N3

>  <Short Description for web display>  (347) 
Pomalidomide-PEG1-C2-N3 is a compound that has been synthesized as a conjugate of an E3 ligase ligand-linker. This compound incorporates the cereblon ligand based on Pomalidomide and a 1-unit PEG link
er, which are commonly used in PROTAC technology. Utilizing Pomalidomide-PEG1-C2-N3, it is possible to design a selective CDK6 PROTAC degrader known as CP-10. CP-10 effectively induces the degradation
 of CDK6, displaying a DC50 value of 2.1 nM[1].

